25
00:01:09.900 --> 00:01:12.820
By over a period of time I mean
between two balance sheets.

26
00:01:12.820 --> 00:01:18.210
So, maybe over a quarter, or over a year,
using something called accrual accounting

27
00:01:18.210 --> 00:01:23.630
which is where recognition is tied to
